Note #6659 gets a similar error, but I think is unrelated, this one is due to a constraint issue, with it calling the constraint as a static function rather than method.  @YilouWang might you be interested in debugging?   Not critical for me, just blocks one UVM test, tests/70regs/80examples/01model/30nofield

